CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper December 5, 1959, pg. 1, reads: "Eagle Scouts - Lynn V. Hooe Sr., Scoutmaster of Troop 93, congratulates Raymond Page and Robert Lavelle on their attainment of Scouting's coveted Eagle Badge during ceremonies at Grace Memorial Presbyterian Church. Looking on is Leonard Payne, assistant Scoutmaster of the troop. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Boy Scout Troop 93 Assistant Scoutmaster Leonard Payne, Eagle Scouts Raymond Page and Robert Lavelle, and Scoutmaster Lynn V. Hooe at Eagle Badge ceremony, Grace Memorial Presbyterian Church
